 * (FileSink, AsyncFileSink).
 * @{
 * @class stc::logger::IRotationPolicy
 * @class stc::logger::SizeRotationPolicy
 * @class stc::logger::TimeRotationPolicy
 * @class stc::logger::CircularRotationPolicy
 * @} 
